title.narrative: Liaoning and Shandong Technical and Vocational Education and Training Project

description.narrative: The revised development objective is to improve the quality and relevance of technical education in project schools in Liaoning andShandong provinces and produce lessons from this experience as a guide for future school reforms and policy development.
